    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "You are right, the `*Shell` classes don't seem to care about the config.\n\nThis updated snippets seems to do it for me:\n\n``` python\nfrom IPython.terminal.ipapp import TerminalIPythonApp\napp = TerminalIPythonApp.instance()\napp.initialize(argv=[])\nprint('colors:', app.shell.colors)\n```\n\nThanks for your help I'll close this issue !\n"
